# pnpm patches directory
# Use `pnpm patch <package>` to create patches for dependencies that need modifications.
# Apply patches via the `patchedDependencies` field in root package.json.
#
# Example:
#   pnpm patch eslint-plugin-react@7.37.5
#   # ... make changes in the extracted directory ...
#   pnpm patch-commit '<path-to-extracted-directory>'
#
# See: https://pnpm.io/cli/patch
